videos.description: Wichita State's Landry Shamet lofts a pass up to Zach Brown for the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Shamet connects with Brown on the oop

videos.description: UCF's B.J. Taylor drives down the paint and knocks down the jumper to earn an opportunity at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Taylor converts contested jumper for and-1 chance

videos.description: Following the miss from Wichita State's Landry Shamet, Darral Willis grabs the offensive rebound and converts the dunk to earn a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Willis converts second-chance dunk

videos.description: Wichita State's Austin Reaves finds Shaquille Morris down low for a layup in the second half.
videos.headline: Reaves' dime sets up Morris' lay-in

videos.description: UCF's Ceasar DeJesus fakes out his defender on a pump fake and knocks down the mid-range jumper.
videos.headline: DeJesus sinks jumper following pump fake

videos.description: UCF's B.J. Taylor drives down the lane and tries putting up a layup but is rejected by Wichita State's Rauno Nurger.
videos.headline: Nurger denies Taylor in the paint

videos.description: UCF's Ceasar DeJesus drives down the lane and sinks a tough layup to earn a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: DeJesus nails layup for and-1 opportunity

videos.description: Wichita State's Shaquille Morris finds Markis McDuffie down low for the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Shockers ball movement leads to McDuffie's slam
